# R3 Reactive Rules (with MessagePipe Boundary)

## Core Rule
- R3 = STATE
- MessagePipe = EVENT

## R3 Usage
- Long-lived observable state.
- UI binds via ViewModels.

## MessagePipe Usage
- One-shot events.
- Past tense naming.

## Forbidden
- Using R3 for events
- Using MessagePipe for state
